d of the official opening of the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 700, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are our top five players to watch:  The tournament's star name is undoubtedly Manchester City forward Alvarez.\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 816, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 784, \"end\": 799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester_City_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.999448936027448, \"rank\": 0.0005513678115388136, \"text\": \"Manchester City\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester_City_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester_City_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 22-year-old was in prolific form last season for Pep Guardiola's side, who he helped to win an unprecedented fourth consecutive Premier League title.\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 971, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 950, \"end\": 964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.682195616479011e-29, \"text\": \"Premier League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That all came after the Cityzens lifted five trophies in 2023 - in Alvarez's first season - by completing the treble of the league, FA Cup and Champions League before claiming the UEFA Super Cup and the FIFA Club World Cup.\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 1196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1116, \"end\": 1132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.621754217354072e-80, \"text\": \"Champions League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\"}, {\"begin\": 1153, \"end\": 1167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Super_Cup\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4229202240336316e-12, \"text\"