bpedia.org/resource/FC_Bayern_Munich\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olise was born to a Nigerian father and French-Algerian mother, which is where his decision to represent France originates.\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2504, \"end\": 2512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2536915306661444e-22, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2589, \"end\": 2595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.317044072331206e-28, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The name that may usurp all others at the Olympics could be that of Thiago Almada.\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2677, \"end\": 2690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thiago_Almada\", \"score\": 0.9999998152616343, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thiago Almada\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thiago_Almada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thiago_Almada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Where expectation will sit upon the shoulders of fellow countryman and Premier League star Alvarez, Almada has a stock that is primed for takeoff.\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2839, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2764, \"end\": 2778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.682195616479011e-29, \"text\": \"Premier League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\